data.description: Step into this dreamy, historic gem just a stroll away from the heart of downtown Newnan. Freshly reimagined in 2021, this home boasts a 2-year-old roof, sleek gutters, updated electricals, and a modern water heater. The original hardwood floors have been lovingly restored to their former glory. Imagine cooking in a kitchen adorned with quartz countertops, chic tiled backsplash, and nearly new stainless steel appliances. The cabinets are also almost new, and the floors are tiled. The dining room is a cozy space to gather, featuring beautifully restored hardwood floors. In the family room, a charming brick fireplace sets the mood, surrounded by more of that gorgeous hardwood. The main-floor master suite is your private retreat, complete with its own deck. The en-suite bathroom is a spa-like haven with a quartz vanity and a beautifully tiled shower. Two additional bedrooms offer ample closet space and share a stylish guest bathroom, complete with a vanity and a tiled shower-tub combo. This home is where historic charm meets modern elegance, all in nearly new condition. Come see for yourself!
